Insider Activity


Individual




Douglas N. Armer



Mr. Douglas N. Armer is Treasurer & Head-Capital Markets at Blackstone Mortgage Trust, Inc.
Prior to joining Blackstone, Mr. Armer was a Managing Director at CT Investment Management Co. As Managing Director, he handled the firm’s capital markets and finance activities. Prior to joining Capital Trust in 2004, Mr. Armer was involved with developing the India-based capital markets group of Global Realty Outsourcing. Previously, Mr. Armer held positions in Corporate Finance at Gerard Klauer Mattison and at PaineWebber Commercial Real Estate Securities.
Mr. Armer holds a B.A. in Political Science, magna cum laude, from the University of Rochester, where he was inducted into the Phi Beta Kappa honor society.



