Treasurer, Managing Director of Blackstone Mortgage Trust (NYSE:BXMT), Armer Douglas N., sells 604 shares worth $18,766
According to Blackstone Mortgage Trust's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Jun 02 06:07 PM, company Treasurer, Managing Director, Armer Douglas N. disclosed selling 604 shares at a cost of $31.07. At the time of this transaction (May 31), this trade was worth $18,766 in total. As of May 31, Armer Douglas N. now owns 54,940 shares in total worth about $1,715,226.8. 
For the last few recent trades made by Blackstone Mortgage Trust (NYSE:BXMT) Treasurer, Managing Director, Armer Douglas N., we have the following information:




SEC Form 4 filing: Apr 28: Sold 530 shares at the rate of $30.71 per share. Total worth of this trade was $16,276. Total number of shares owned as of Apr 28 were 55,544
SEC Form 4 filing: Feb 28: Sold 590 shares at the rate of $31.22 per share. Total worth of this trade was $18,420. Total number of shares owned as of Feb 28 were 56,074
SEC Form 4 filing: Jan 31: Sold 596 shares at the rate of $30.43 per share. Total worth of this trade was $18,136. Total number of shares owned as of Jan 31 were 56,664




